title: PSX NTSC The Weakest Link 2001 (CCD)
description:
PSX NTSC The Weakest Link 2001 (CCD)

Test your brain power as you take center stage in the home version of the hit game show. Think fast on your feet to answer host Anne Robinson&#039;s tough trivia questions correctly or you&#039;re toast.  Know your foes&#039; weaknesses and play your voting strategy right, because there&#039;s only one word for losers in this arena: "Goodbye!"

Image made with Clone CD Version 3.3.4.1

You Can burn with Clone CD, or Nero 8 works well too.

PowerISO made several coasters for me (Failed burns). Don&#039;t know if I&#039;m doing something wrong with PowerISO or not.

This is my first upload, and I plan to make others of my favorite PSX games!  All NTSC!

Any suggestions from veteran Torrenters would be appeciated.  Enjoy and please Seed!!
